Repeat: sl 1 wyib, drop yo off needle, k4, sl 1 wyib, drop yo

drop next stitch to front of work, k2, pick up dropped stitch and knit it; slip 2 wyib, drop next stitch to front of work, slip same 2 stitches back to the left-hand needle, pick up dropped stitch and knit it; k2
k2, (sl 1 wyib, drop yo) twice, k2
